                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="feature-heading">
              Espera tranquilamente tu ida a la u sin preocupaciones
              <br />
            </h3>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="half-side">
        <div class="screenshot-wrap 2">
          <img
            src="imgs/MockupWeb2.jpg"
            loading="lazy"
            alt=""
            class="screenshot"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section less-top">
    <div class="container flex mob-switch">
      <div class="half-side img">
        <div class="screenshot-wrap left">
          <div></div>
          <img
            src="imgs/MockupWeb.jpg"
            loading="lazy"
            alt=""
            class="screenshot left"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="half-side right">
        <div class="div-block-11">
          <div class="label">Seguridad</div>
          <div class="section-heading">
            Viaja con confianza de quienes te acompañan
          </div>
          <div class="section-subheading">
            Gracias al respaldo de las instituciones universitarias y del
            sistema de verificación, la seguridad vial ha alcanzado niveles sin
            precedentes. Los conductores, quienes son estudiantes como usted,
            son rigurosamente verificados mediante la validación de su identidad
            estudiantil y gubernamental.
          </div>
          <div id="aniDiv"><AnimatedBeamDemo client:load /></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <style>
      :root {
        /*
    Colores RideSharing
    */
        --darkest-text: #1d1d1d;

        --purple: #5d17eb;
        --dark-purple: #350d85;
        --light-purple: #d3c2f6;
      }

      .section.overflow {
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding-top: 124px;
        padding-bottom: 0px;
        overflow: hidden;
        z-index: 0;
        background-image: radial-gradient(
          circle closest-side at 20% 50%,
          var(--light-purple) 1%,
          #ffffff 60%
        );
      }
      .container {
        z-index: 9;
        max-width: 90%;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        position: static;
      }
      .container.flex {
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        align-items: flex-start;
        width: 1200px;
        display: flex;
      }

      .half-side.left {
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        width: 42%;
        padding-right: 48px;
        display: flex;
      }

      .label {
        color: var(--purple);
        letter-spacing: 0.1rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.49);
        background-image: linear-gradient(
          to right,
          rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5),
          rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25)
        );
        border-radius: 70px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        padding: 10px 16px;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        line-height: 100%;
        display: inline-block;
        box-shadow: 0 3px 8px -4px rgba(185, 196, 171, 0.46);
      }

      .section-heading {
        color: var(--dark-purple);
        margin-top: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-size: 3.3rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        line-height: 105%;
      }
      .section-subheading {
        opacity: 1;
        color: var(--dark-text);
        margin-top: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        line-height: 150%;
      }

      .feature-block {
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);
        border-radius: 3.5px;
        align-items: center;
        margin-top: 4px;
        margin-top: 4px;
        padding: 8px 24px 8px 0;
        display: flex;
      }

      .feature-icon-wrap {
        background-color: var(--light-purple);
        box-shadow: none;
        color: var(--darkest-text);
        border-radius: 1000px;
        flex: none;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        width: 45px;
        height: 45px;
        display: flex;
      }

      .feature-icon {
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        width: 24px;
        height: 24px;
        display: flex;
      }

      .feature-heading {
        color: var(--dark-text);
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 0;
        margin-left: 20px;
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        font-weight: 400;
        line-height: 150%;
      }

      .half-side {
        width: 50%;
      }
      .screenshot-wrap {
        height: 920px;
        position: relative;
        left: 24px;
        overflow: visible;
      }

      .screenshot {
        -webkit-text-fill-color: inherit;
        background-clip: border-box;
        border: 1px solid #e5e3e0;
        border-radius: 12px;
        max-width: 940px;
        height: auto;
        display: block;
        position: absolute;
        top: 0%;
        bottom: 0%;
        left: 0%;
        right: 0%;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 11px 40px -5px rgba(75, 32, 19, 0.19);
      }

      .container.flex.mob-switch {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: flex-end;
        align-items: flex-start;
        width: 1300px;
      }

      .screenshot-wrap.left {
        height: 880px;
        left: -4%;
      }

      .screenshot.left {
        display: flex;
        position: relative;
        left: -45%;
        right: 0;
        bject-position: 40% 50%;
        border-radius: 10px;
        max-width: 940px;
        height: auto;
        min-height: 0;
        max-height: none;
        margin-right: 0;
        padding-right: 0;
        position: absolute;
        top: 0%;
        bottom: 0%;
        left: -38%;
        right: 0;
        box-shadow: 0 11px 40px -5px rgba(75, 32, 19 0.19);
      }
      .div-block-11 {
        margin-left: 100px;
        animation: fade-in 1s cubic-bezier(0.48, 0.03, 0.79, 0.66) both;
        animation-timeline: view();
        animation-range: entry 90% cover 50%;
        background-image: radial-gradient(
          circle closest-side at 20% 35%,
          var(--light-purple) 20%,
          #ffffff 100%
        );
      }

      .half-side.img {
      }

      img {
        vertical-align: middle;
        display: inline-block;
      }

      @keyframes fade-in {
        0% {
          opacity: 0;
          padding-top: 50px;
        }
        100$ {
          opacity: 1;
          padding-top: 0px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </div>
</main>
